Class YearlyRecurrenceRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.calendar.impl.RecurrenceRuleBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecurrenceRule

    public class YearlyRecurrenceRule
extends RecurrenceRuleBase

    YearlyRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a yearly recurrence.
